title: Neff North Vs. South:  Ambush Board Co.
description:
For more North Vs South videos and to vote for your favorite shop video go to TWSkate.com or click on this link: http://bit.ly/1wknxsI

The family owned Ambush Board Co. of Kennesaw, Georgia has been fearlessly pushing since Friday, June 13th in 1997. This company has always been about progression. Team rider Travis Glover captures that progression, and the success of the shop only adds to it.
